title: Mocoosy Foam Glow Sticks Party Packs, 32 PCS LED Light Up Flashing Sticks with 3 Modes, Colorful LED Neon Toys Glow in the Dark Party Supplies for Wedding, Raves, Concert, Birthday, Halloween
features: Glow In The Dark Party Essentials: This set includes 32 LED foam glow sticks, each measuring 16 inches. Lightweight and easy to hold, these glowsticks are equipped with bright, eye-catching LEDs that can be waved for hours without causing hand fatigue. Perfect for creating a lively atmosphere and adding extra excitement to any part.

Long-Lasting and Durable: Crafted from environmentally friendly foam and pearl sponge, these light up sticks party pack are flexible, safe, and kid-friendly. Each LED stick is powered by three high-quality batteries, ensuring up to 8 hours of vibrant glow. Enjoy your party all night long without worrying about the lights dimming!

Easy to Use and Safe: Our LED glow sticks feature a simple On and Off switch function. Activate by removing the insulating plastic sheet and pressing the button for a dazzling neon glow. Turn them off when not in use to conserve battery life. Each foam stick is individually packaged for easy distribution and convenient storage.

Versatile Light Modes: Each neon foam glow stick features three dynamic lighting modes: fast flashing, slow flashing, and alternating flashes in green, red, and blue. With just a press of a button, you can choose your favorite mode to light up the party to create a mesmerizing light show that will leave your guests in awe.

Endless Glow Party Fun: Perfect for both indoor and outdoor events, these foam glow sticks bulk add a magical glow to any celebration, especially after dark. Ideal for birthdays, weddings, concerts, camping, Halloween, sports events, raves, and more. Enhance your party vibe with these glowing accessories that promise endless fun!
